The paper deals with a machine learning problem of learning a function that links conditional distributions to target values. This problem is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and statistics (cs.ST). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
